                            Installation instruction
                            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
1. FreeBSD
~~~~~~~~~~
a. From binary (txz) package

   Use package manager to install/remove application.

b. From source package

   Build and install:
   # tar -xzf cmmapi-0.1.tar.gz
   # ./configure
   # make
   # make install

   Remove:
   # make uninstall

2. Linux
~~~~~~~~
a. From binary (deb, rpm, txz) package

   Use package manager to install/remove application.

b. From binary (bin) package

   Install:
   # ./cmmapi-0.1-i586.bin

   Remove:
   # /opt/cmmapi/uninstall

c. From binary (tar.gz) package

   Install:
   # cp cmmapi-0.1-i586.tar.gz /opt
   # cd /opt
   # tar -xzf cmmapi-0.1-i586.tar.gz
   # cd cmmapi
   # ./create_links
            or
   # tar -xzf cmmapi-0.1-i586.tar.gz
   # cd cmmapi
   # ./install

   Remove:
   # /opt/cmmapi/remove_links
   # rm -r /opt/cmmapi/
            or
   # /opt/cmmapi/uninstall

d. From source package

   Build and install:
   $ tar -xzf cmmapi-0.1.tar.gz
   $ ./configure
   $ make
   # make install

   Remove:
   # make uninstall
